{%- if direction_score %}
### 🧭 方向性推定 詳細

<table class="tech-table">
<thead>
<tr><th>市場</th><th>判定</th><th>スコア</th><th>テクニカル</th><th>F&G</th></tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>米国</td>
<td>{{ direction_score.us.emoji }} {{ direction_score.us.label }}</td>
<td>{{ "%+d"|format(direction_score.us.score) }}/10</td>
<td>{{ "%+d"|format(direction_score.us.tech_score) }}/6</td>
<td>{{ "%+d"|format(direction_score.us.fg_score) }}/4</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>日本</td>
<td>{{ direction_score.jp.emoji }} {{ direction_score.jp.label }}</td>
<td>{{ "%+d"|format(direction_score.jp.score) }}/10</td>
<td>{{ "%+d"|format(direction_score.jp.tech_score) }}/6</td>
<td>{{ "%+d"|format(direction_score.jp.fg_score) }}/4</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>

<p style="font-size:0.8rem;color:gray;">
Fear & Greed: {{ direction_score.fg_raw }} ({{ direction_score.fg_label }})
スコアは参考値です。投資判断の最終確認は各自でお願いします。
</p>
{%- endif %}

</details>

